<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
        -webkit-border-radius: 100px;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
        width: 9px;
        height: 16px;
        overflow: visible;
        width: 16px;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-button {
        height: 0;
        width: 0;
    }

    body::-webkit-scrollbar-corner {
        background-clip: padding-box;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        border: solid #fff;
        border-width: 3px 0 0 3px;
        -webkit-box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14);
        box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14);
        background: transparent;
    }

    body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px;
        border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        -webkit-border-radius: 100px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
        background-clip: padding-box;
        border: solid transparent;
        border-width: 1px 1px 1px 6px;
        min-height: 28px;
        padding: 100px 0 0;
        -webkit-box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
        box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
        background-clip: padding-box;
        border: solid transparent;
        border-width: 0 0 0 2px;
    }

    body::-webkit-scrollbar-track-piece {
        background-clip: padding-box;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        border: solid #fff;
        border-width: 0 0 0 3px;
        -webkit-box-shadow: inset 1px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14), inset -1px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
        box-shadow: inset 1px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14), inset -1px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
    }

    #container {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #45a049;
    }

    #up {
        width: 100%;
        height: 90%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: start;
        align-items: center;
        background: #eee;
    }

    #down {
        width: 100%;
        height: 10%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    #down form {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
    }

    #name {
        font-size: 25px;
        width: 8%;
        height: 60%;
        border-radius: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    #content {
        font-size: 25px;
        width: 70%;
        height: 60%;
        border-top-right-radius: 50px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 50px;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
        border-top-left-radius: 10px;
    }

    #down input[type="submit"] {
        width: 10%;
        height: 60%;
        font-size: 25px;
        background: #62e669;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    #down input {
        outline: none;
        border: none;
    }

    #tit {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: white;
        margin: 10px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 10%;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: #45a049;
    }

    #comments {
        width: 100%;
        height: 90%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: start;
        align-items: center;
        background: #eee;
        overflow-y: scroll;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .comment {
        width: 100%;
        height: 10%;
        display: flex;
        font-size: 30px;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
        margin: 10px;
    }

    .index {
        width: 5%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: orange;
        color: white;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .user {
        width: 15%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .commentcontent {
        width: 80%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: start;
        align-items: center;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    #windowcontainer {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .7);
        z-index: 100;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    #wincontent {
        width: 40%;
        height: 50vh;
        position: fixed;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        display: flex;
        z-index: 101;
        align-items: end;
        background-color: white;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    #wintext {
        width: 100%;
        height: 80%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 30px;
        color: black;
        text-align: center;
    }

    #winbtn {
        width: 100%;
        height: 20%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 30px;
        color: white;
        background: #45a049;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    #winbtn:hover {
        background: #62e669;
    }
</style>

<body>


    <div id="wincontent">

        <div id="wintext">
            <p>本網站為期末計概報告使用，<br><br>請勿張貼與威士忌無關之內容，謝謝。</p>
            <p>若有違反，本網站將保留刪除留言之權利。</p>
        </div>

        <div id="winbtn">
            我同意
        </div>

    </div>
    <div id="windowcontainer">
    </div>

    <div id="container">
        <div id="up">
            <div id="tit">威士忌互動留言板</div>
            <div id="comments">
                {{{recordmail}}}
            </div>

        </div>
        <div id="down">
            <form action="/uploadmessage" method="post">
                <label for="name" style="font-size: 30px;color:white">名字</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" id="name" required>
                <label for="content" style="font-size: 30px;color:white">內容</label>
                <input type="text" name="content" id="content" required>
                <input type="submit" value="送出">
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>



</body>

<script>
    var windowbtn = document.getElementById('winbtn');
    var wincontent = document.getElementById('wincontent');
    var windowcontainer = document.getElementById('windowcontainer');

    windowbtn.addEventListener('click', () => {

        wincontent.style.opacity = "0";

        windowbtn.style.opacity = "0";

        windowcontainer.style.opacity = "0";

        wincontent.style.zIndex = "-1";

        windowbtn.style.zIndex = "-1";

        windowcontainer.style.zIndex = "-1";

        windowcontainer.style.display = "none";

        windowcontainer.style.backgroundColor = "none";
    })
</script>

</html>